import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react";
import {
  ListGroup,
  ListGroupItem,
  Row,
  Col,
  Form,
  FormInput,
  FormGroup,
  FormCheckbox,
  FormSelect,
  Button
} from "shards-react";

import {useHistory} from 'react-router-dom';

const LoginForm = () => {
  <ListGroup flush>
    <ListGroupItem className="p-3">
      <Row>
        <Col>
          <Form>
            <FormGroup>
              <label htmlFor="namaAdmin">Nama Admin</label>
              <FormInput id="namaAdmin" placeholder="Nama Admin" />
            </FormGroup>
            <FormGroup>
              <label htmlFor="password">Password</label>
              <FormInput id="password" placeholder="Password" />
            </FormGroup>
            <Button type="submit" className="d-flex ml-auto mr-auto ml-sm-auto mr-sm-auto mt-3 mt-sm-4">Login as Admin</Button>
          </Form>
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </ListGroupItem>
  </ListGroup>
}

export default LoginForm;
